# 06 â€” Docker dev environment

Use this when starting stacks, debugging `/catalog` 502s, or onboarding on **Windows + Docker Desktop**.

**Requires PowerShell 7 (`pwsh`)** â€” not Windows PowerShell 5.1. Repo `.vscode/settings.json` configures Cursor/VS Code to use `pwsh` for terminal and tasks.

## First run (mock â€” no sibling repos)

In Cursor: **`Ctrl+Shift+P` â†’ Tasks: Run Task â†’ `Cursor: Quick start mock + open UI`**

Or PowerShell from repo root:

```powershell
.\scripts\dev-up.ps1 -OpenUi
```

This writes mock `.env`, starts all services detached, waits for health, opens http://localhost:5180.

## Real upstreams (KB-IHMS + EC-OPS)

Clone sibling repos:

```
../KB-IHMS
../EC-OPS
```

Cursor task: **`Cursor: Real dev environment (full)`**  
(prompts for paths; default `../KB-IHMS`, `../EC-OPS`; credentials `admin` / `Password1!`)

## Stop

Cursor task: **`Cursor: Stop stack`** or `.\scripts\stop-stack.ps1`

## Verify

Cursor task: **`Health: Verify stack`** â€” checks `/health/upstreams` and catalog.

Manual:

```powershell
Invoke-RestMethod http://localhost:8000/health/upstreams | ConvertTo-Json
```

## Stack modes

| Mode | `.env` upstream URLs | When |
|------|----------------------|------|
| Mock (default) | `http://ihms:8080`, `http://ecops:8002` | CI, local demo, no sibling repos |
| Real | `http://host.docker.internal:5000`, `:8002` | Interview/demo with real KB-IHMS + EC-OPS |

**Never use `localhost` in `.env` when orchestrator runs inside Docker** â€” use Docker service names (mock) or `host.docker.internal` (real).

## Scripts map

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `scripts/dev-up.ps1` | Mock stack, detached + health wait |
| `scripts/full-stack.ps1` | Mock stack, foreground logs |
| `scripts/real-upstream.ps1` | Real upstreams; add `-Detached` for background |
| `scripts/start-upstreams.ps1` | Start KB-IHMS + EC-OPS sibling Docker |
| `scripts/ecops-token.ps1` | Fetch JWT into `.env` |
| `scripts/health-check.ps1` | Upstreams + catalog diagnostic |
| `scripts/stop-stack.ps1` | `docker compose down` |

Bash equivalents (`*.sh`) exist for Linux/macOS and cloud agents.

## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| `/catalog` 502 "All connection attempts failed" | Run `mock-stack.ps1 -Check` or `real-upstream.ps1 -Check`; fix `.env` URLs |
| WIDGET-001 instead of real products | Real upstream mode not active â€” check `IHMS_BASE_URL` |
| Port bind errors | Set `ORCHESTRATOR_PORT` / `UI_PORT` in `.env` |
| EC-OPS 401 on confirm | Re-run task **EC-OPS: Refresh token + restart orchestrator** or `.\scripts\refresh-ecops-token.ps1` |

Full reference: [docs/DOCKER.md](../docs/DOCKER.md)

